'''曼弗雷'''（'''Mapfre'''，{{IPA-es|ˈmafɾe}}，官方排字：'''MAPFRE'''，台灣官方譯名：曼福）是一家總部位於[[西班牙|西班牙]][[馬哈達翁達|馬哈達翁達]]的[[保險公司|保險公司]]。是西班牙主要保險公司之一<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=conewsstory&refer=conews&tkr=MAP%3ASM&sid=alQ5Z3Pc4PHg|title=Sabadell, Iberia, Metrovacesa, Repsol, Impresa: Iberian Preview|last=Gore|first=Gareth|date=3 November 2008|work=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]]|accessdate=2009-01-29|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023205748/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=conewsstory&refer=conews&tkr=MAP:SM&sid=alQ5Z3Pc4PHg|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时也是[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]最大的非人寿保险公司。

2007年10月以15億歐元的價格買下美國汽車保險公司Commerce Insurance Group。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/feeds/afx/2007/10/31/afx4281926.html|title=Mapfre acquires US insurer Commerce for 1.538 bln eur|date=31 October 2007|work=[[AFX_News|AFX News]]|publisher=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|accessdate=2009-01-29}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

2010年10月買下英國旅遊保險公司InsureandGo。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.e-tid.com/News-Home/Mapfre-taps-InsureandGo%E2%80%99s-online-know-how.aspx|title=Mapfre taps InsureandGo’s online know-how|date=8 October 2010|publisher=e-tid.com|accessdate=2011-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101209180455/http://www.e-tid.com/News-Home/Mapfre-taps-InsureandGo%E2%80%99s-online-know-how.aspx|archive-date=2010-12-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.insurancetimes.co.uk/story.asp?sectioncode=69&storycode=387593&c=1|title=Mapfre acquires Insure and Go|date=1 November 2010|publisher=Insurance Times|accessdate=2011-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.postonline.co.uk/post/news/1863836/mapfre-swoops-insure|title=Mapfre swoops for Insure & Go|date=1 November 2010|publisher=Post Online|accessdate=2011-02-05|archive-date=2013-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227002008/http://www.postonline.co.uk/post/news/1863836/mapfre-swoops-insure|dead-url=no}}</ref>

